=== Launching QEMU with guests ===
qemu-system-aarch64 -machine virt,gic-version=3,virtualization=on,iommu=smmuv3 -cpu cortex-a57 -m 2G -smp 4 -nographic -serial mon:stdio -no-reboot -d guest_errors \
